Yet another time of migration (blog-wise)&hellip;
TextDrive -&gt; Joyent -&gt; TextDrive 2 My web hosting has been a little up in the air recently (see Slashdot: Joyent Drops Lifetime Account Holders).
I paid a few hundred bucks several years back (2005) for &ldquo;lifetime&rdquo; web hosting at what I perceived to be a cool up and coming company (read: they claimed to be pushing to support a lot of the flashy new web tech that wasn&rsquo;t well supported by most shared web hosting providers at the time).
